<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Nitak ai ishtaiyopikma
 Chihowa h čt yakni moma
 Hushmi na lu čt bila he;
 H čsh w čnnihincha hi oke.

[V2]
 ∆≤banumpa shitilema
 H čsh ahaŐĪshwa tuk ok čno,
 Falam čt misha oh ia,
 H čchim ahancha hi oke.

[V3]
 Nana pal čmmi chinto k čt
 H čchi onutuyulakma,
 Ilb čsh čt h čsh yahaŐĪya kia,
 Nanta'k osh chi apela wa.

[V4]
 Klaist shitilema chia h čt
 Yummak oŐĪ chi y čmohma he,
 Kanima a hlakoffa he
 Iiksho ka he mak oke.

[V5]
 Nitak h čch illa chiŐĪ hok čt
 Chekosi h čchim  čla chiŐĪ;
 Chihowa im anumpa haŐĪ
 Ishtaiyopi ish hakla chiŐĪ.

[V6]
 H čchi okchaŐĪya taiyakla
 Hopoyuks čt aiokchaŐĪya
 On ch čf čt chuŐĪk čsh isht ahnit
 Yimmit h čchi okchaŐĪyashke.</lyrics>
